TO COMPILE:
make

TO RUN:
./mp2

STEERING:
W - pitch up
A - roll left
S - pitch down
D - roll right
space - speed up
C - speed down

OTHER:
+ - ocean level up
- - ocean level down
/ - day/night speed up
* - day/night speed down  (note: this can go negative and reverse day/night)

Press escape to exit.



Source code Included:
mp2.cpp - Contains the main glut and opengl calls used make the window.  This also moves the sun and moon
	vertices and light sources.

plane.cpp - Contains code used to move, roll, and pitch the camera.

mountain.cpp - Contains code used to draw the mountain and the water, and raise the water level.

vector.h - Contains a struct for a 3D float vector.
